abstract: Online organizers set Saturday as the date to spread the Occupy Wall Street to cities around the world. In Italy, protesters started early by storming into the offices of Goldman Sachs.
snippet: Online organizers set Saturday as the date to spread the Occupy Wall Street to cities around the world. In Italy, protesters started early by storming into the offices of Goldman Sachs.
lead_paragraph: Online organizers have set Saturday as the date to spread the Occupy Wall Street protests to cities around the world.

headline.main: As Calls for Protests Go Global, Italy Jumps the Gun
